# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# Magento core files deployed by Composer (magento/magento2-base and
# friends). None of this is our code — it's regenerated automatically
# by `composer install` / `make magento-install`. Only app/code/ (our
# module) and the project's own scaffolding files should be tracked.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------
/.htaccess
/.htaccess.sample
/.user.ini
